section.houseRulesSubtitle: You'll be staying in someone's home, so please treat it with care and respect.

html.htmlText:
Important!!!
It is completely forbidden:
- Exceed the allowed number of guests.
- Commercial and non-commercial events, parties and photography or recording sessions on the property without authorization.

In case of non-compliance with the above, the eviction will be processed without the right of return.
***
